AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ This module is used everywhere one alarm shall be generated when one input photocell becomes false and this photocell signal has to be checked during transfer. If the alarm is enable, the photocell may not be deactivated by means of breaking the ray. This FB also check the consistency of the photocell. During the period we are sure the photocell must be activated (transfer), the input of the photocell is checked on activity. Alarm is disable from HMI, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level and do action in the Alarm summary. When the conditions to generate the alarm is disappear, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level that the alarm can be reset. The alarm is reset by means of the AlarmResetPB signal. ================================================================================
